{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"c304f7fa3d3dec88367652df1ac39a7619ed3ed10af98bd0634d8c5e7aa5b404","slug":"skill-4","location":"/handbook/agent/skill.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"技能工程","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/handbook/agent/skill.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/handbook/agent/skill.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"skill.md","url":"/skill-73ad0c34cf9afe8e83dc044ec7bdaff8.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"从对话上下文提炼Skill","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"i5cgojgPEf"}],"identifier":"id-skill","label":"从对话上下文提炼Skill","html_id":"id-skill","implicit":true,"key":"oBy0XjtDaF"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用一个纯净的对话完整地做一遍事情，然后在结束的时候复盘你的方法，再把这个方法提炼到项目的 Skill 里。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"Ic7F1MmNTi"}],"key":"mbmgcSW2WZ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在这个“纯净的对话”里，我们只做一件事情，且这件事情都由 AI 接管，人类只让 AI 按既定流程一步一步走。这样的对话环境捕捉的人类的隐式知识的非常干净的，因此可以给 AI 提供良好的环境捕捉 Skill。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"HbeEbtheCh"}],"key":"UDx4h1vSdT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"比如说，你让 AI 写一个新功能，先增加一个开发者文档，增加一个代码模块，再对应增加一个单元测试模块，再增加一个用户文档说明。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"f2a9VWx5U1"}],"key":"k2brB3hlJy"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一个对话结束以后，就可以要求 AI“总结我们刚才的工作流程”，然后“遵循 Agent Skill规范（规范网页地址）写成 xxx 文件”。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"WnXhZY5Xef"}],"key":"jTHU5Bsoj8"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有两个重点补充说明。一是一定要从实际工作中总结，因为这是经过有效验证的。二是要让 AI 自己总结，人手动维护的 Skill 大多比较缺乏必要细节而质量糟糕。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"aIYvhXO8OB"}],"key":"H0IHSsZH3j"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为Skill准确命名和分类","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"AiattIp9Et"}],"identifier":"id-skill","label":"为Skill准确命名和分类","html_id":"id-skill-1","implicit":true,"key":"WBrlzaxwan"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一定要准确地定义 Skill 的名称和分类。命名和分类实际上就是在理解这个流程到底是什么，也为了以后持续改进做准备。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"MnAyy4cJkH"}],"key":"EEYy8sju8B"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"分类尽可能遵循量潮的标准领域划分，比如“编程 code”、“写作 write”、“数字资产 asset”、“数据工程 data”、“文档工程 docs” 等。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"qYjV4JPJlt"}],"key":"dbbYY3f46V"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"命名尽可能简单直接，比如“发布 release”、“计划 plan”、“设计 design”、“格式 format”等等。\n这样一眼就可以知道这个 Skill 在做什么。建议把领域名称作为前缀区分，如“docs-format”是文档格式维护 Skill。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"vlv5205W4G"}],"key":"Mzb4XfbtiN"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人类可以不纠结 Skill 的具体文本，但是一定要维护好命名、描述等元数据。","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"VwD0wel36x"}],"key":"KU0GVP91wk"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"只保留实际效果好的Skill","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"fPl8qzKs5E"}],"identifier":"id-skill","label":"只保留实际效果好的Skill","html_id":"id-skill-2","implicit":true,"key":"Ia3pdulpmn"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"低质量的 Skill 对于人机都是负担。所以质量低的 Skill 要及时抛弃。","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"fmMs3ELpG8"}],"key":"Y7rwNeoPMF"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一类是流程不完善。这类通常要回到人机交互模式下慢慢摸索，而不是继续让这个低质量 Skill 做事。","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"GUddyH1o1c"}],"key":"FK9vQHaE2k"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一类的 Skill 机制不够合适，需要显式、刚性的触发条件。比如上文提到的文档格式 Skill 其实更适合内置成一个自动化工具，只要维护 Markdown 文档就要触发。","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"key":"MqiHFvGVlI"}],"key":"GZTrfe6liO"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Skill 的舒适区是规则引擎写的不够灵活、又实际上存在标准规范的。比如基于 Git 的 commit、release 等流程，又或者是基于 TDD 的标准开发流程。这类流程要最大限度地 Skill 化，减少人类纠正 AI 的错误。","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"H0wSd8Dz4A"}],"key":"Gbewn0dS6j"}],"key":"hMSsRIkzO7"}],"key":"tOGuEznpzL"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}